            },
            "description": "Sensing wavefront aberrations induced by Earth\u2019s atmosphere is a pivotal part of adaptive optics systems. In this project, we simulate and build a prototype of a new type of wavefront sensor (WFS) using the differential Optical Transfer Function (dOTF) technique. The expected advantage of the dOTF WFS approach over other methods is its low cost and relative simplicity.",
